  <h2>Why owners trust us in Lutz</h2>
  <p class="lead-2">Lutz offers a quieter, more spacious lifestyle on the northern edge of Tampa, with lakes, larger lots, and a semi-rural feel — all while staying minutes from the Veterans Expressway, Tampa Premium Outlets, and top schools. Families are drawn to the space and the strong school zones.</p>
  <p>We manage single-family homes, properties on acreage, and newer subdivision homes across Lutz's 33548, 33549, and 33558 ZIP codes spanning the Hillsborough–Pasco line. Larger properties have unique needs, and we handle everything from lawn and well systems to standard maintenance.</p>
  <h3>What we handle for Lutz owners</h3>
  <ul class="checks">
    <li>Marketing to families seeking space and good schools</li>
    <li>Thorough screening for dependable, long-term tenants</li>
